ingredients.ingredient: ½ cup Borden® Cheddar and Monterey Jack Shreds
½ cup jalapeno-flavored cream cheese, softened

cookingTips: Mix cooked chicken with both cheeses and jalapeno-flavored cream cheese for a creamy, spicy filling
Place small spoonful of filling in center of wonton wrapper, then fold into triangle and seal edges with water
Spray wontons with cooking spray before baking to achieve a golden, crispy exterior without deep frying
enrichment.coachingPrompt: Demonstrate proper wonton folding and sealing, explain filling ratios to prevent bursting, and show how to achieve crispiness without oil.
